    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To demonstrate that import Mesalazine (ASACOL速) is non-inferior to the reference drug,
      marketed Mesalazine, regarding the primary endpoint (rate of non-emergence of bloody stool),
      in patients with Ulcerative Colitis in remission, treated for 48 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
